122
00:07:35,000 --> 00:07:39,000
 at this point in Israel's history, there have been two kings.

123
00:07:39,000 --> 00:07:46,000
 Israel originally had no king, but they said, "God, we want to be like the rest of the people around us, so give us a king."

124
00:07:46,000 --> 00:07:50,000
