00:42:00,000 --> 00:42:03,000
 and a purpose from the king.

619
00:42:03,000 --> 00:42:08,000
 And father, I pray that we'd run hard and fast after you.

620
00:42:08,000 --> 00:42:12,000
 Not confident in our own abilities or our gifts,

621
00:42:12,000 --> 00:42:16,000
 but just confident in the fact that we can run hard and fast

622
00:42:16,000 --> 00:42:17,000
 in the job that you've given us

